data.description:
Investment opportunity with the best price per foot in the community! Conveniently situated just minutes away from the Raytheon corporation and the McQuinney Howell Wright Park Municipal Golf Course, this townhome offers both comfort and accessibility.The Jade 2 C model presents a spacious and inviting layout, seamlessly connecting the kitchen, dining area, nook, and family room. Ideal for entertaining or quiet moments, the open spaces are designed to flow harmoniously.

Upstairs, you'll discover a thoughtfully placed game room that provides an additional area for relaxation and leisure. The highlight of the upper level is the expansive master bedroom, boasting impressive dimensions of 14'2x19'4. The master suite is complemented by a generously sized walk-in closet, adding to the convenience and functionality of the space.The kitchen features stunning granite countertops that provide both style and functionality, while each bathroom is adorned with luxurious marble countertops.
